item.title: Who is Alexandre Gagnon?
item.description: Alexandre Gagnon is a con artist from Quebec, Canada. Alex has a paper trail of scams on the internet due to his activities on HackForums and other websites. If you are familiar with Team Fortress 2 trading, this is the same Alex that runs Mannco.store. The staff on the project are friends who helped Alex perform scams on his previous aliases. Alex’s modus operandi is to run DDoS attacks on competitor websites.
